.RE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Perform SCSI part of hotplug\&. It\*(Aqs executed from a separate workqueue after EH completes\&. This is necessary because SCSI hot plugging requires working EH and hot unplugging is synchronized with hot plugging with a mutex\&.
.PP
